data.title: Tony Tur on LinkedIn: Morning shoots in brickell. Nice thing about being here early besides…
data.meta_description: Morning shoots in brickell. Nice thing about being here early besides parking is watching the colors of light change through sunrise.
data.text:
"The past cannot be changed; the future is still in your power." - #HughWhite Unfortunately, going to work can cause fear and anxiety for many individuals. However, it is a common occurrence, and people should have confidence that they will be protected from bullying or retaliation. Working is a fundamental part of life for most of us, but being able to do so in a safe environment should never be a second thought. As the old saying goes, "safety first," which is often shouted by corporations. However, most reviews based on internal audits, policy, and practice usually rate safety far lower, safety coming in at the 9th objective in strategy and operations.
